type: decisions
timestamp: '2025-12-24T19:24:57.957385+00:00'
summary: AI-evaluated issue completeness with user override
---

AI-evaluated issue completeness with user override
## Context
User wants Claude to assess whether an issue has sufficient detail to begin planning elicitation with reasonable confidence. The threshold is practical: "can we start meaningful requirements elicitation?" rather than a rigid checklist.

## Rationale
- Flexible assessment rather than boolean checkbox requirements
- User retains final judgment with 4 options: post clarification, add details inline, proceed anyway, skip
- Professional tone for GitHub comments maintains project credibility
- User MUST have option to request Claude draft a clarification comment

## Related Files
- commands/plan.md (will be extended)

